Christy Onyenaturuchi Ucheibe (amụrụ na 25 Disemba 2000) bụ onye Naijiria na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-agba ọsọ n'etiti maka otu Portuguese Benfica
Ucheibe gbara bọọlụ maka Nasarawa Amazons n'afọ 2018.
Na 14 Febụwarị 2020, Ucheibe bịanyere aka na klọb Portuguese Benfica na nkwekọrịta afọ atọ na ọkara.
A họpụtara Ucheibe maka 2014 FIFA U-17 Women's World Cup na 2018 FIFA U-20 Women'sWorld Cup. Na asọmpi ikpeazụ ọ gbara egwuregwu atọ site na mbido.
